Poster Specifications:

Immerse yourself in flawless edge-to-edge printing with our posters. Crafted expertly in the USA on 200 GSM paper, each piece lacks borders, allowing the design to shine. Choose from three sizes: 16×12 inches, 24×16 inches, and 36×24 inches. Please note, we sell our posters without frames, giving you the freedom to select your preferred framing style.

Framed Canvas Specifications:

Our framed canvas artworks not only exude beauty but also offer hassle-free hanging. Each pre-framed canvas includes an attached hook for effortless installation. Available in three sizes: 16×12 inches, 24×16 inches, and 36×24 inches, these canvases consist of a blend of 25% cotton and 75% polyester at 300 GSM, featuring a sturdy 1.5-inch wooden frame. The semi-matte finish adds a touch of elegance to your wall decor.

Unframed Canvas Specifications:

Craft your personalized masterpiece with our unframed canvas prints. These sublimation printed artworks, available in three sizes: 16×12 inches, 24×16 inches, and 36×24 inches, require custom framing to showcase your unique style. Rest assured, our fade-resistant UV archival inks and protective coating ensure the longevity and durability of these canvas prints, guarding against scratches and spills effectively.
